ill expire in", "bbox": [162.5, 1308.6, 1072.7, 1329.4]}, {"text": "2033. The Company’s lease commitment is approximately $116 million over the lease term. In conjunction with", "bbox": [162.5, 1333.6, 1101.0, 1354.4]}, {"text": "its lease of the new headquarters building, the Company will be vacating three leased facilities adjacent to its", "bbox": [162.5, 1358.6, 1072.7, 1379.4]}, {"text": "current Princeton headquarters facility. Based on certain clauses in the lease, the Company is considered the", "bbox": [162.5, 1383.6, 1065.0, 1404.4]}, {"text": "owner, for financial statement reporting purposes, during the construction period, and recorded $17.4 million in", "bbox": [162.5, 1408.6, 1094.6, 1429.4]}, {"text": "construction in progress assets and a corresponding offset in other long-term liabilities.", "bbox": [162.5, 1433.6, 889.4, 1454.4]}, {"text": "86", "bbox": [627.1, 1484.1, 647.9, 1504.9]}]}